cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper is primarily focused on action recognition using deep convolutional neural networks (CNNs) on depth videos. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel CNN model for feature learning, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of multi-view dynamic images involves the manipulation of 3D space, which could be categorized under cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also proposes an action proposal approach to address spatial occurrence variation, which could be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper deals with video data, which could be categorized under cs.MM (Multimedia).
